Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.09,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日もこの胸は張り詰めたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.04,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学後に 約まれて 君を見てる Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.58,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとあしらいは揃わないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:13.76,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,続くから　内緒だよ　少し約め Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.84,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知りすぎて知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.31,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえないフリが上手になって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.56,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ深呼吸一つしたら眼を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.99,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自問自答やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:34.68,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何気なくおはようって言っちゃてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.83,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽きるくらい全部君がほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.27,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートは涙でいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:47.15,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋のいろはとがまた分かってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.39,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何度も繰り返すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.92,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸前でまだ次回へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.66,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sweetな乙女心は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.24,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あいにく取り扱ってないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.69,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ これが「I LOVE YOU」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.09,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是心中悸动不停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.04,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后仍一直看着你 Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.58,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步调总是无法一致
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:13.76,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还会继续 这是秘密哦 一点点慢慢来 Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.84,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太过了解而毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.31,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装听不到也越装越好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.56,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 深呼吸一次之后睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.99,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那自问自答了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:34.68,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事地对他说「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.83,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要你的全部想要到自己都受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.27,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中载满泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:47.15,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道恋爱的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.39,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论重复多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.92,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却总在最后一刻退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.66,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那甜甜的少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.24,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有被操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.69,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 这就是「I love you」?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:06.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:11.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫　果然你家里有什么不该有的东西存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:17.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜总觉得睡不着 睁开眼睛以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:21.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方 好像有个小孩站在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:28.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎鸡蛋我要吃散的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:36.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 弟弟的性格和雫不怎么像啊 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这怎么搞得像你家一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:15.95,tk-title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(723,558)}暑  假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:19.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要补习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 他居然第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是校方搞错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的时候一定要好好的预习了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来啦 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能考到689分已经很厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:41.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的全科目加起来连300分都没到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又要补考了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿比基尼的话我会很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同学 你真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你脑子里在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是不会去海边玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把球技大会想参加的项目填好交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水 你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对卷子上的题目还有疑问 去找老师问问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:24.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能在这些娱乐项目上提高点兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我这个好友在的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许她压根没把你当朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(168,64)\frz6.931}问题15
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(557,93)\frz8.167}请用50个以内的文字简单描述主人公此时此刻的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.591\pos(821,294)}错失嫁入豪门的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.172\pos(890,421)}人生陷入绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这道题目给我这个分？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们已经下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我现在没心情看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在上班时间内 请继续工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊这道题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是错误的但是也不是正解所以才给这个分的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:56.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在你的答案之中完全感受不到失恋的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份感情难以抑制无处诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 我的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老师的主观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个回答我接受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 我知道了 好缠人啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:22.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同学你一定还没有了解失恋的痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 我被春甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你喜欢上我的时候再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能让他喜欢我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为什么我会喜欢春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师给你加分了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…诶 卷心菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:11.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狠狠的瞪了一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么瞪着人家就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没瞪她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得别人躲着你的原因大概就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你害怕了所以搞得别人也害怕起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:35.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢你微笑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干烧虾仁 干烧虾仁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田春…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢你微笑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢 非常喜欢 非常 非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.08,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的特别节目看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.95,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.04,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 东西掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:30.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢 十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:34.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:41.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉 一点都不恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺帅的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公鸡 名字是名古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然整个人爆红了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟春同学也挺帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近待人态度友善多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生们也对他有好感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像雫说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不瞪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不用做 别人也会主动来搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是眼神的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:21.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同学 春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以教我们功课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.13,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关我什么事 那种事自己做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.52,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.92,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.65,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同学好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.85,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和之前没什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:35.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到人气暴涨之后 说什么大家都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借宠物排解寂寞的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊 夏目同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样嘛=3=
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同学最近都被女生包围着很难接近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传回来 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接踢进去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田  是相反的球门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:07.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这里 看这里 春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的反应真是变化超大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前还没有人敢靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水不会是吃醋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这就是吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好坦率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.65,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全天球技比赛 加油B班 为了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小水 你根本没碰过球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:05.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到夏目同学体育是强项
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子排球怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:19.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小水多动一点 或许还有机会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边吉田可是超级活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为太热血 打到裁判了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？春同学呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田能一直这样顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田国中时也不来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:46.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的时候发生打架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果引发了大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙看起来很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的人也很怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事之后 吉田就不来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说这次能顺利维持就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都有过去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿佐这么担心春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:11.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你才和春说上话不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我欠他一份人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师叫我们去准备器材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？现在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 你们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个班级 没怎么说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热 好想喝水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.23,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去叫老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把什么扔到别人头上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头肿起来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好糗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 算了 我不想看到你 快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:32.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我认得你 上次闯到C班的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女生打出鼻血是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想流鼻血试试吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太嚣张了 一年级的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她非要被你们这群人说「给我滚」这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 打架了 打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 情况是不是有些不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…已经够了吧 快停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们道歉就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你们几个在干什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么能为了阻止纠纷反而将事情闹得更大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然连我也落到被老师追着跑的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里做错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也遇到过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识到的时候 周围的人都用可怕的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都想不明白为什么会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里做错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能说你的做法就是完全正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我知道春是个很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道春是个很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总用一天 大家一定也会知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的雫像英雄似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄在我陷入危机的时候跑过来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入危机的应该是对方才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头弄脏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 下一场比赛就要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待…待会见了 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是赢了比赛的话 暑假一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:07.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 春赢了称不上打赌的赌约
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目朝子 要从这么高的地方跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号吉田春 要从更高的地方跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.77,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就把目标锁定在红点鲑和真鳟上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼会把从上游飘下来的饵食作为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让鱼饵这样漂在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看它们游来游去的我全都抓来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是野人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:07.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小夏目 能帮我洗一下这个锅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 溪流垂钓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿三哥和春是表兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 这家伙的老爸是我老妈的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:36.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为高中离我家比较近 今年开始就借住在我那了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.29,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水知道这些事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直以为是亲哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的哥哥另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 说起他那个哥哥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿三哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一个劲地乱说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 已经回到店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把行李拿下来 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把春叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是睡了好久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:36.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去把特产分一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在店里稍等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 最近新建了一个交友网站哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:59.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见到人家就跑开 真是太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:05.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿佐同学 这个人是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢阿三哥钱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才春突然逃了出来…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:19.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满善 我貌似被误认为从你那里抢钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是春同学的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫吉田优山 春给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他就是白天说的春的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便提一句 是我借了人家钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…你把西瓜切开了吗 我还想玩砸西瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 想不到春居然有这么多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 那家伙表现还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:52.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了水谷同学 还来上学了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没帮什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:11.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那家伙是个笨蛋 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 春同学为什么会逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事啊 很平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是个严重的兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为吉田的哥哥是什么人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的是个普通的善良人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要买东西 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:46.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 今后春也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得是个怪哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然赶不上弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:05.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是啊 为什么老做些对人家心脏不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙一起玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:08.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩砸西瓜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一直幽怨地闷在这里想着砸西瓜的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 放开我 会疼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是严重的兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要躲着他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事 别什么事都问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:50.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:04.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是生气要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我家也有西瓜 要砸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸好了雫 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为自己很了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却发现自己对他几乎一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别什么事都问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:39.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么 让他露出那么可怕的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:40.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚才说了那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:52.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫总会帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该回报你一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:58.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:07.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这个…总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:13.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸西瓜是这样玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:14.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事 以后知道了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:20.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:02.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 你一对着镜头就紧张过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:03.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
